cess anomalies.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"Moderately increased io_util which could contribute to upstream performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"io_util normal_p99 of 0.84, fault_p99 0.21 with p99 change ratio of 1.2\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThese observations and hypotheses focus on the anomalies most likely contributing to the fault during the specified period.", "current_hypothesis": "EmailService Pod lifecycle anomaly causes performance degradation."}
